{"tid":2425404,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"達叔唔死都死左啦 有咩好嘈？ 提防踩港撚引戰分化","createTime":"2021-02-27T10:24:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-28T01:07:02.000Z","uid":98431,"like":65,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"900eeedc41dce1918a6e97744e5e969ebae3e3ba","tid":2425404,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T10:24:13.000Z","msg":"我無特別感覺 唔認為要特別可惜 或者特別去眨低佢<br />\n<br />\n反而有批藍屍五毛借連登個名黎放負踩港 咁講唔過去 所以都係決定留言屌多次佢地老母<br />\n<br />\n今朝果條借達叔踩港既仆街一早扑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟據佢既支那邏輯 689都係人黎 我地要尊重同珍惜佢 因為隻狗曾經登報屌八九六四<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">傻既都知講唔通啦 完全就係借題發揮 偷換 概念 轉移視線</span><br />\n<br />\n踩港矮化香港人先係呢班仆街既目的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fe2ee3f96c9ae0308fed9f71b809dd9c4ff7f49","tid":2425404,"uid":98431,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T10:27:06.000Z","msg":"堆五毛藍屍學晒熱狗d衰野<br />\n<br />\n一黎就霸左個道德高地 再入連登數<br />\n<br />\n根本兩樣野黎 屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e165a49eaeb33f0908ff7e620c2e4c19aadcb766","tid":2425404,"uid":98431,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T10:32:58.000Z","msg":"自推十連<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0051dfdc98cf45a2eb27f179a30cb233b87a12ad","tid":2425404,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T10:33:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c45b4a3ef7f75b902a6100277b99c0bbccb3dc27","tid":2425404,"uid":98431,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0051dfdc98cf45a2eb27f179a30cb233b87a12ad","tid":2425404,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T10:33:35.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T10:36:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔該<br />\n<br />\n呢排班五毛無工開 全部都係抗疫失敗既新聞 應該好等錢洗"},{"pid":"f1856dce61f1745f52e9eaa6f2aa85d713f4b1fa","tid":24254